data.description: Amazing opportunity to own this stunning 3 bed/2.5 bath ranch home w/almost 2000 sq. ft. of living space and 2 car garage in the Parkway West School District at an incredible price. This meticulously maintained home features a new furnace and A/C (2012), new windows (2009) and a newer roof. Enter this home and be welcomed by the warm finishes in the living and dining room.The open floor plan is evident when you walk into the cozy family room w/fireplace that overlooks the large kitchen/breakfast room that includes 2 pantries, double ovens, electric cooktop, refrigerator and microwave (included). Beyond the kitchen is the fabulous main floor laundry room w/half bath. The home also boasts a large master bedroom suite w/a full bathroom and a generous sized walk in closet. The basement is as clean as it gets and has a ton of space that is ready for your finishes. Beautiful landscape, corner lot, fenced back yard, HPP and a neighborhood pool complete the package. At this price, this home won't last long!
